                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10149" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0349</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">223 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">双碳为引，聚势谋远：中国巨石“点石成金”，擎举ESG火炬启新程</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Guided by Dual Carbon Goals, Gathering Momentum for a Sustainable Future: China Jushi Transforms Stone into Gold, Raising the ESG Torch to Ignite a New Chapter</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曹聪，施程阳，张炫铻（通讯作者），费梓聪，余鑫乐，丁裕哲，姚明明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">巨石集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国巨石；双碳目标；ESG实践；技术创新；绿色转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">China Jushi; Dual Carbon Goals; ESG practices; Technological Innovation; Green Transition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例聚焦中国巨石在双碳目标引领下的ESG（Environmental，Social，Governance）实践历程。2023年以来，中国巨石在“双碳”目标引领下，以ESG战略为核心，通过技术创新、产业链协同和全球化布局，实现了从行业标杆到国际典范的跨越。从埃及建厂与混合所有制改革为起点到如今面对欧盟《企业可持续发展尽职调查指令》等严苛法规，巨石以“无废工厂”建设、供应链碳追溯和本土化人才计划突破贸易壁垒，交出了一份完美的ESG答卷。巨石通过分层级ESG管理架构强化执行，并推动全产业链“共治”。其中，中国巨石能够取得成功的关键因素既有早期的技术创新和智能制造，也有后来的绿色转型和全产业链整合，其ESG战略经历了从思想萌芽到正式实施，最后向全行业拓展。巨石以“互帮互助”理念深化全球合作，带动当地就业与产业升级，形成“内外互补”双循环模式。截至目前，巨石凭借ESG实践荣获“中国上市企业ESG最佳案例”等多项荣誉，为新兴市场企业提供了“经济效益与社会价值共生”的可行路径。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study examines China Jushi’s ESG (Environmental, Social, and Governance) practices under the “dual carbon” policy framework. Since 2023, the company has leveraged its ESG strategy as a core driver, transitioning from an industry leader to a global benchmark through technological innovation, supply chain collaboration and international expansion. The journey began with pivotal initiatives such as establishing production facilities in Egypt and implementing mixed-ownership reforms. Facing stringent regulatory requirements including the EU Corporate Sustainability Due Diligence Directive, China Jushi has demonstrated resilience through its “zero-waste factory” model, carbon footprint tracking across supply chains, and workforce localisation programmes, delivering exemplary ESG performance. The company has reinforced governance through a multi-tiered ESG management structure while championing industry-wide “collective governance”. The key factors contributing to China Jushi&#39;s success include early technological innovation and intelligent manufacturing, as well as subsequent green transformation and full industrial chain integration. Its ESG strategy has evolved from the initial conceptual stage to formal implementation, and finally expanded to the entire industry. Guided by principles of mutual cooperation, China Jushi has fostered global partnerships that stimulate local employment and industrial development, creating an integrated “dual circulation” operational model. The company’s achievements have been recognised through prestigious accolades including the “ESG Best Practice Award for Chinese Listed Companies”, establishing a replicable framework for emerging market enterprises to balance economic returns with societal value creation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《责任与可续管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">运用三重底线理论分析中国巨石遭遇的内外部危机和挑战；学习治理成熟度模型和生态现代化理论的构建</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
